Developer Terms of Use
des:
Cubo Ai is the only smart baby monitor have proactive A.I. for baby’s sleep, safety, and memories.
And now, with our Amazon Alexa integration, you can go hands-free and watch Cubo’s live stream right on your Echo Show.

To get started, enable the skill and link your Cubo account. In seconds, you'll be able to watch your baby’s crib by asking Alexa:

“Alexa, Show me Oliver” 

With Alexa, Cubo is smarter than ever, you can project baby’s live video feed to other devices to allow hands-free access as you tackle your to-do list.

Google Wi-Fi users,
please disable DNS rebinding protection for this skill to work. Please follow the instructions in this link: https://support.google.com/wifi/answer/9144137?hl=en
